kquote><br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d480b45f98bfaff53a5568789e9c350bfb2144","tid":438053,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/183013_0b9d79fb78a8d9ed8b90c1f54b50ffb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F183013_0b9d79fb78a8d9ed8b90c1f54b50ffb6.jpg&h=e6accfe0&s={SIZE}\" />lm</blockquote><br />\n無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你玩到邊   我玩到冷戰 卡關 超難打 基本打到一半就死曬 0課有古科里布加個尼米茲<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解會無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd39a5c12398c529dc95d18d1d0d121f579eaf9","tid":438053,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"玩緊第3代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8443e7b2d90e0b92327f039151271f41bb9ea19","tid":438053,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"4好玩好多 多好多變化"},{"pid":"cc8ade17b69f2bb68f9df8d53d58407729ff8442","tid":438053,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:46:37.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"a8854c0f777b0e8121675d62e1749299c47da08d","tid":438053,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T00:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4好玩好多 多好多變化</blockquote><br />\n4代要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42ae763d7dabab0c2da564a57df7826d271f103","tid":438053,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4好玩好多 多好多變化</blockquote><br />\n4代要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n8蚊姐 或者玩破解 我之前都係玩破解 依加玩原版  其實有樂趣D<br />\n可以慢慢存章升將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fa9bb02fa4c1e34f4a8a8568c99f95d9bec6e0","tid":438053,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4好玩好多 多好多變化</blockquote><br />\n4代要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n8蚊姐 或者玩破解 我之前都係玩破解 依加玩原版  其實有樂趣D<br />\n可以慢慢存章升將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3同4有乜唔同？<br />\n點較中文？"},{"pid":"f1b5783765ffcbdac80fb0f4353eda1352673c1b","tid":438053,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4好玩好多 多好多變化</blockquote><br />\n4代要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n8蚊姐 或者玩破解 我之前都係玩破解 依加玩原版  其實有樂趣D<br />\n可以慢慢存章升將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3同4有乜唔同？<br />\n點較中文？</blockquote><br />\nIOS DL落黎就係中文好似 入面直接有得轉 唔記得左 但白痴都識攪<br />\n4無得自己養自己一隻將<br />\n但分金銀銅三區既將 銅3招技 銀多一招 金再多一招 多出黎既技係自己簡學咩都得 分五級 技能方面多過3 亦都唔再全部都純係加攻打大力D咁<br />\n地形方面減少左平地 唔係只係打平原戰 強化左空軍<br />\n增加左科技樹 比你點野 慢慢加強各類野既能力  有挑戰模式 打過左就可以用6折買勁既將 演習等等比你拎章同過關<br />\n唔同國家有自己特有既超級兵種 例如超坦 超炮 超兵 超潛 超戰列 超航母等等 每個國家會有1-2種<br />\n打咩1943 1939 個D世界大戰 可以送錢比盟友洗供肥佢 唔洗次次都自己由頭打到落尾"},{"pid":"fe6562c401a5490fe723947b18a14128cec286e8","tid":438053,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"仲有任務 拎資源咁"},{"pid":"ffbb6e1bf246473ca126782d79ec16ee00b16651","tid":438053,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/183013_0b9d79fb78a8d9ed8b90c1f54b50ffb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F183013_0b9d79fb78a8d9ed8b90c1f54b50ffb6.jpg&h=e6accfe0&s={SIZE}\" />lm</blockquote><br />\n無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你玩到邊   我玩到冷戰 卡關 超難打 基本打到一半就死曬 0課有古科里布加個尼米茲<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解會無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地中海戰役卡關<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94f75003538e4047bac658aa2abaeed9fdedabf","tid":438053,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/183013_0b9d79fb78a8d9ed8b90c1f54b50ffb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F183013_0b9d79fb78a8d9ed8b90c1f54b50ffb6.jpg&h=e6accfe0&s={SIZE}\" />lm</blockquote><br />\n無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你玩到邊   我玩到冷戰 卡關 超難打 基本打到一半就死曬 0課有古科里布加個尼米茲<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解會無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地中海戰役卡關<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊關黎 依加我打到冷戰第5關過唔到 存緊資料升D奇觀 所以科技卡住左 根本打唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2621f401ca75235a15e720e3304a0a40d46d60","tid":438053,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:19:30.000Z","msg":"An下載落黎係英文，setting度又無得轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cd42757e9ab52c6b04364e60ee39f79e18c6c5","tid":438053,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite